"title": "5917: plans",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5917",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Designs or schemes, prepared in advance of doing something. Scripture indicates the sovereign plans of God and the varied plans of men and women.</p>\n<h2>God's plans</h2>\n<h3>For judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:11\">JER 18:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num33:55-Num33:56\">NUM 33:55–33:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:25-2Kgs19:26\">2KI 19:25–19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:14-Job23:16\">JOB 23:14–23:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:1-Isa25:2\">ISA 25:1–25:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:26-Isa37:27\">ISA 37:26–37:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:3\">JER 26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:17\">LAM 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:3\">MIC 2:3</a>ISA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic14:24-Mic14:27\">14:24–14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:12\">ISA 19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:17\">ISA 19:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:8-Isa23:9\">ISA 23:8–23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:20\">JER 49:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:45\">JER 50:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:11-Mic4:13\">MIC 4:11–4:13</a></p>\n<h3>For salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11\">EPH 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:5\">PSA 40:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:40\">HEB 11:40</a></p>\n<h3>For the tabernacle and the temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:30-Exod26:37\">EXO 26:30–26:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:11-1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:11–28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:18-1Chr28:19\">1CH 28:18–28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:10-Ezek43:11\">EZK 43:10–43:11</a></p>\n<h2>God's plans are revealed to his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:7\">AMO 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:30\">EXO 26:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:20-Jer49:21\">JER 49:20–49:21</a></p>\n<h2>God's plans are always fulfilled</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:2\">JOB 42:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:11\">PSA 33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:18-Isa5:19\">ISA 5:18–5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:24-Isa14:27\">ISA 14:24–14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:11\">ISA 46:11</a></p>\n<h2>God may sometimes reverse his plans</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:3\">JER 36:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:5-Jer18:10\">JER 18:5–18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:3\">JER 26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:10\">JON 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Plans of the wicked</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:5-Ps64:6\">PSA 64:5–64:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:1-2Sam17:4\">2SA 17:1–17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:10-2Kgs16:11\">2KI 16:10–16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:2\">PSA 140:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:22\">PRO 14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:32\">PRO 30:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1\">ISA 30:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:12\">JER 18:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1\">MIC 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:12-Matt28:13\">MAT 28:12–28:13</a></p>\n<h2>Plans of the righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:5\">PRO 12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:2\">1CH 28:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:6\">PSA 14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:22\">PRO 14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:5\">PRO 21:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:8\">ISA 32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:13\">ROM 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:24\">ROM 15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:15-2Cor1:17\">2CO 1:15–1:17</a></p>\n<h2>Plans and the role of counsellors</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:22\">PRO 15:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:4-Ezra4:5\">EZR 4:4–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:18\">PRO 20:18</a></p>\n<h2>Malicious plans</h2>\n<h3>Against other people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:25\">1SA 18:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:10\">1SA 23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:3\">EST 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:4\">PSA 140:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:30\">JER 49:30</a></p>\n<h3>Against God's servants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:18\">JER 18:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:15\">MAT 22:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:10-John12:11\">JHN 12:10–12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:23-Acts9:24\">ACT 9:23–9:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:42-Acts27:43\">ACT 27:42–27:43</a></p>\n<h2>Human plans are subject to God's will</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:15\">JAS 4:13–4:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:10\">PSA 33:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:4\">PSA 20:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:8\">PSA 140:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:4\">PSA 146:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:1-Prov16:3\">PRO 16:1–16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:9\">PRO 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:21\">PRO 19:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:30\">PRO 21:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:10\">ECC 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:10\">ISA 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:3\">ISA 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:7\">JER 19:7</a></p>",
